{"tid":584903,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ONEPIECE 海賊王 ワンピース897 情報","createTime":"2018-03-08T07:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T07:08:50.000Z","uid":3020,"like":6,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8badd3c4707282a07ae3d98e85aa8cb78ab2ff41","tid":584903,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T07:41:50.000Z","msg":"897話。扉頁：斯坦森出現在海爾丁的部隊中<br />\n【注：斯坦森就是兩年前在肥皂泡群島和雷利曾經關在一起的那個巨人，大媽回憶篇也出現過童年的他和海爾丁在一個畫面】<br />\n在可可亞島的大媽團和山治都在等待。 SUNNY號到達了可可亞島邊上。<br />\n鏡世界：抱著布蕾的貝克慕斯和路飛正在奔跑。他們找到了一面鏡子，然後出去了。出來的同時，貝克慕斯的墨鏡飛了出去。他發現外面是滿月，然後開始變身月亮獅子形態。<br />\n歐文攻擊貝克慕斯，路飛從貝克慕斯的手中飛了出來。<br />\n大媽團開始攻擊路飛，路飛踢中了雷森的臉。<br />\n山治在半空中抓住了路飛，然後開始使用空中步行離開。<br />\n在他們走遠之前，圓（一個人物） 從空中擊倒了他們。<br />\n路飛和山治掉到了地上的同時，傑爾馬到達了。<br />\n傑爾馬擊散了包圍可可亞島的大媽艦隊，然後傑爾馬的艦隊登場，伊治，蕾玖，尼治，勇治等人登陸援助路飛和山治。<br />\n下週不休刊<br />\n<br />\n英文情報原文：<br />\nTItle: Pekoms' Cacao Island Escape Plan<br />\n<br />\nCover: Stansen from Hajrudin's crew is shown.<br />\n<br />\nThe Big Mom pirates are waiting, and so is Sanji. The sunny has arrived just outside of Cacao. In the Mirro-World, Pekoms is running with Luffy and Brulee in his arms. They get to the mirror, and go through. They come out, and Pekoms' sunglasses fly off as he comes out of the mirror. He realizes the full moon is out and begins to turn into his Sulong form. Oven attacks Pekoms. Luffy comes flying out of his arms. The Big Mom pirates begin to attack Luffy, and Luffy kicks Raisin in the face. Then, Sanji grabs Luffy in mid-air and begins to sky walk with him away. Before they get too far, Yuen knocks them out of the air. Luffy and Sanji are on the ground , when Germa arrives. Germa blows up the Big Mom pirate fleet surrounding Cacao. Their fleet is shown, and Ichiji, Niji, Reiju, and Yonji come to land to assist Luffy and Sanji.<br />\n<br />\nNo break next week"},{"pid":"475db1d922379cf7cb814d6132c1c1f512dd529e","tid":584903,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:25:50.000Z","msg":"圓乜水<br />\n兩個見聞超高手都打得中？"},{"pid":"80b50f79378b3f2c0301c574a38e0f519411e5c5","tid":584903,"uid":2644,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"又拖一話<br />\n<br />\n越睇落去　就越掛住當年美食的基佬既節奏　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db36ce4ef524b5ffa61db3a5d69da529cccba03","tid":584903,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:52:34.000Z","msg":"我都唔記得左係月圓添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"443fd8431d39b0d15679d1ee062a3dc35db8a757","tid":584903,"uid":33104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1db36ce4ef524b5ffa61db3a5d69da529cccba03","tid":584903,"uid":25635,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:52:34.000Z","msg":"我都唔記得左係月圓添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:03:11.000Z","msg":"原來成日帶黑超係伏筆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1853129a14d5dcc8127403011da527bcbec7fce","tid":584903,"uid":13215,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"80b50f79378b3f2c0301c574a38e0f519411e5c5","tid":584903,"uid":2644,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"又拖一話<br />\n<br />\n越睇落去　就越掛住當年美食的基佬既節奏　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:13:33.000Z","msg":"以前有美食做balance 日子好好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e3f8b8b93bdb7cd8469bf1d2f8aee3199e0ff6","tid":584903,"uid":159183,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T09:20:05.000Z","msg":"個期個個星期都好多野睇<br />\nop 火影 死神 美食 暗殺教室 <br />\n仲有妖尾 七原罪 間唔中既有hxh<br />\n美食同op我直頭係個個星期追情報<br />\n而家見連登有情報post先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似少左好多野睇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/